  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ContentProvider.IWebFeature
    Interface required for each feature.
    IContentComponent
    Implementations of this interface are to be used as content components for IndexPage.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContentProvider
    All features (components intended to be displayed in the content area of DefaultUI) should be registered here.
    UnimplementedView
    Generic view for features that are not implemented yet.
    WelcomeView
    Default view.
